        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h3 id="題目連結"><a href="#題目連結" class="headerlink" title="題目連結:"></a>題目連結:</h3><p><a href="https://neoj.sprout.tw/problem/3401/">https://neoj.sprout.tw/problem/3401/</a></p><h3 id="解題邏輯"><a href="#解題邏輯" class="headerlink" title="解題邏輯:"></a>解題邏輯:</h3><p>等差數列的概念，a為有n項，公差為1，b為這數列的結果<br>計算出來的結果要小於b，才不會燃料耗盡</p><h3 id="程式碼"><a href="#程式碼" class="headerlink" title="程式碼:"></a>程式碼:</h3><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// Sprout OJ No<span class="number">.3041</span>-超級貓貓星際漫遊-<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">a, b = <span class="built_in">map</span>(<span class="built_in">int</span>, <span class="built_in">input</span>().split(<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (a + <span class="number">1</span>)*a / <span class="number">2</span> &lt;= b:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Maow oil enough&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Maow oil not enough&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
